item.title: Code for full black
item.dc:creator: @KillerConnor KillerConnor
item.description:
@KillerConnor wrote:

Find “Client.java” in your server folder.
Open it, and search for “public void moo” ( Control+F)
Under public void moo() { addSkillXP((12*playerLevel[19]), 19); addItem(1927, 1); sendMessage("You get some milk"); }
UNDER -> Put the code

public void fullblack() { addItem(1077, 1); addItem(1125, 1); addItem(1165, 1); addItem(1195, 1); addItem(1297, 1); sendMessage("You get full black"); }

Think i missed some things…couldn’t find them.
